Figs. 3A, 3B and 3C are illustrations of a control link,
showing variation of elastic deformation depending on loading
direction;

Fig. 4 is a graph showing a relation between a load applied
to a control link and an elastic deformation appearing on the
control link;

Fig. 5 is a graph showing a relation between a load inputted
to a control crankshaft and a bending deformation appearing on
the control crankshaft;

Figs. 7A and 7B are views similar to Figs. 6A and 6B, but
showing the bending deformation of the control crankshaft
appearing when a load is applied thereto in a second direction;

Figs. 8A and 8B are views similar to Figs. 6A and 6B, but
showing the bending deformation of the control crankshaft
appearing when a load is applied thereto in a third direction;
